headline: Why Robinhood Stock Was Scorching Hot Last Month
summary: June is a sluggish month for some, but it sure was active for next-generation brokerage Robinhood Markets (NASDAQ: HOOD).  Not every development was a boon for Robinhood, however.  Investors sold out of Robinhood on the news.
